snippet.title: The Sims 4 City Living: Official Festivals Trailer
snippet.description:
Take your Sims to festivals throughout the city where they can watch street performers, enter competitions, and meet different walks of life.
Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/16994
